job_history.work_description: Manages the overall operation of the branch to include the Personal Bankers and Teller staff primarily focused on creating a positive work environment, community development, driving sales, increasing growth & profitability, and providing accurate and superior customer service.

Builds relationships with customers while performing financial transactions including paying, receiving, and cash control duties; opening and servicing accounts, seeks to uncover financial needs, minimize loss, reduce risk, and deliver accurate and superior customer service and lending requests handling more complex situations and deeper profiling over time.

Functions as the Customer Service Manager ensuring a solid operational foundation; builds relationships with customers while performing financial transactions including paying, receiving, and cash control duties; seeks to uncover financial needs, minimize loss, reduce risk, and deliver accurate and superior services.

interests: Coast Young Professionals with the Gulfport Chamber Of Commerce
